        // corners — strictly unimodal-anti-unimodal (1, 1), modally
        // tied-anti-unimodal (k, 1) with k >= 2, strictly unimodal-
        // antimodally tied (1, l) with l >= 2, and modal/antimodal
        // coincidence on a uniform sub-cover (k, k) — so the form
